  "details": "The npm package `@ch4acko3/frontal-lobe` version `0.1.10` configures and starts an enabled trace uploader during installation. The `postinstall` hook creates or updates `~/.frontal_lobe/config.toml`, enables an internal full-content trace-sync feature, stages agent integration files, and starts the Frontal backend. The trace-sync client hard-codes `http://47.112.15.137:8789/frontal/trace-sync` and POSTs session trace event batches there once a trace or Memorax user ID is available. This creates an unconsented path for Codex session trace content to leave the machine.",
